-- ING Investment Management Appoints New Head of Project Finance
-- B y   S t e p h e n   M o r r i s
-- 2013-03-27T12:52:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-27/ing-investment-management-appoints-new-head-of-project-finance.html
ING Investment Management Co., the
money management unit of  ING Groep NV (INGA) , has appointed Alistair
Perkins as head of project finance.  Perkins was hired from Dexia Management Services Ltd.,
where he was head of restructuring and asset sales, according to
an e-mailed statement from the company. He will report to Han Rijken, head of fixed income insurance, it said.  “There is considerable investment potential for European
pension funds and insurance companies in developing debt
financing for long-term capital projects such as energy, natural
resources and infrastructure projects,” Jelle van der Giessen,
chief investment officer for insurance at ING IM, said in the
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
